        <![CDATA[<h1>20260324总结</h1><p>作者：D-Sketon（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="跨文件不引用头文件实现函数跨命名空间类的调用">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%b7%a8%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6%e4%b8%8d%e5%bc%95%e7%94%a8%e5%a4%b4%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6%e5%ae%9e%e7%8e%b0%e5%87%bd%e6%95%b0%e8%b7%a8%e5%91%bd%e5%90%8d%e7%a9%ba%e9%97%b4%e7%b1%bb%e7%9a%84%e8%b0%83%e7%94%a8"></a>
跨文件(不引用头文件实现函数跨命名空间类的调用)
</h1><div class="highlight" linenumbers="true"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//使用using定义一个函数指针变量(以输出函数为例)
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">using</span> <span class="n">Out</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)(</span><span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">string</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//------函数1.cpp----
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">Out</span> <span class="n">put</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//------函数2.cpp----
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kt">void</span> <span class="nf">out</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">string</span><span class="p">){</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">string</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><ul>
<li>这样就可以实现文件的不引用调用函数了</li>
</ul>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-03-24首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>My Notes</a>，最后修改于2026-03-24</p>]]>
